name: FTB Network
description:
The design of FTB project stems from the team's in-depth thinking on the
essence of Finance and defi.The defi platform protocol developed by the decentralized
automatic market making defi financial technology component based on FTB is
committed to providing encrypted currency,decentralized lending services and
supporting most popular digital assets in the world. FTB allows global users to access,
borrow and repay anytime, anywhere.
